item.title: GoogleCTF Beginner's Quest 2019 - Home Computer
item.author: shiny-labs@kylma.fr (shiny-labs)
item.description: Description Blunderbussing your way through the decision making process, you figure that one is as good as the other and that further research into the importance of Work Life balance is of little interest to you. You’re the decider after all. You confidently use the credentials to access the “Home Computer.” Something called “desktop” presents itself, displaying a fascinating round and bumpy creature (much like yourself) labeled “cauliflower 4 work - GAN post.
